|  Developer       | -----------------> |  Bitbucket Repo     | ----------------------> |   Bitbucket CI/CD |
+------------------+                    +--------------------+                          +------------------+
                

          Developer Generates Keys
                   |
                   v
       +------------------------+
       | Public/Private Keypair |
       +------------------------+
                   |
                   v
+-------------------------------------------+
| Encrypt Snowflake Private Key using GPG   |
