+-------------------------------------------+
                   |
                   v
       +---------------------------+
       | Store .secret in Bitbucket|
       +---------------------------+

During CI/CD Pipeline Runtime:
--------------------------------
+---------------------------+       +--------------------------+
| Read .secret file         | <---> | Use env vars for         |
|                           |       | GPG passphrase & keys    |
